    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Paninvest Tbk provides banking and multi financing products and services in Indonesia. It operates through Life Insurance and Business Consulting Service; Banking and Multi-Finance; Trade and Services; and Tourist segments. The company offers Sharia banking products and services; financing and mutual funds services; and death, whole life, annuity, endowment, endowment combine, universal life, unit-linked, personal accident, and health insurance products. It also provides business consulting, management, and general administration services; trading and services; and management consulting services in the field of archives. The company was formerly known as Pt Panin Insurance Tbk and changed its name to PT Paninvest Tbk in May 2014. PT Paninvest Tbk was founded in 1973 and is headquartered in Jakarta, Indonesia.",
